
'''Tengana Afahye''' yɛ afehyia afahyɛ a ahenfo ne wɔn manfo a wɔn wɔ Tongo mpɔtam no di<ref>https://tourghana.com/ghana-festivals/</ref><ref>https://touringghana.com/festivals/</ref>. Wɔn a wodi afahyɛ no ne Bulungufo, Winkingofo ne Pwalugufo a wɔn wɔ Atifi Apuei fam wɔ Ghana. Afahyɛ no san nso yɛ afahye a Talensifo nso di<ref>https://ghanaemberlin.de/travel-tourism/festival/</ref><ref>https://ghananation.com/tourism/The-Upper-East-Region.php</ref>. Wodi afahyɛ no wɔ Bosome a edi kan no mu<ref>https://www.slutchtours.com/?page_id=21</ref><ref>http://ghanakey.com/ghana-festivals.html</ref>.

